# FeedPulse AI — Environment Variables
# Copy this to .env and fill in your API key

# Google Gemini API key (get free at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey)
GEMINI_API_KEY=your-api-key-here

# The AI agent works in fallback mode without this key —
# it will still search posts and query trends, just without
# the LLM generating natural language responses.
